<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>New Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .otp-code { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #27ae60; text-align: center; margin: 25px 0; letter-spacing: 3px; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #27ae60; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    .warning { color: #e74c3c; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>New Verification Code Requested</h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

  <p>We received a request for a new verification code for <strong>{{schoolName}}</strong>.</p>

  <p>Here is your new verification code:</p>

  <div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>

  <p class="warning">This code will expire in 10 minutes. Previous codes are no longer valid.</p>

  <p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Complete Verification</a>
  </p>

  <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>The School Management Team</p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} School Management Platform. All rights reserved</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>